===Etymology===
Same word as {{och-l|酖|tr=*l'ums|to poison (v.); poison (n.)}} (e.g. in ''{{w|Zuozhuan}}'', "Xi 30"[https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E5%B7%A6%E6%B0%8F%E5%82%B3/%E5%83%96%E5%85%AC#%E5%82%B3_30]), [[exopassive]] of {{och-l|沈|to put poison in liquid|id=1}} (e.g. in ''{{w|Rites of Zhou}}'' [https://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=en&id=37265]) ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). See {{zh-l|沈|tr=-}} & {{zh-l|沉}} for further etymology.

